title: Willie Nelson & Family - Honeysuckle Rose (mp3@320Kbps)
description:
Honeysuckle Rose: Music From The Original Soundtrack (Expanded, 1980)  Country

Honeysuckle Rose (also known as On the Road Again) is a 1980 romantic drama film directed by Jerry Schatzberg and starring Willie Nelson. In 1981, Willie Nelson was nominated for an Academy Award for Best Original Song for "On the Road Again". Amy Irving won a Golden Raspberry Award for Worst Actress.
